<figureCitation box="[151,311,187,214]" captionStart="FIGURES 228–247" captionStartId="22.[151,264,1860,1884]" captionTargetBox="[157,1425,191,1832]" captionTargetId="figure-16@22.[151,1436,181,1836]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURES 228–247. Male genitalia. 228–233―Anaceratagallia (Anaceratagallia) aciculata, 234–236―A. (A.) kungradica, 237–238―A. (A.) aciculata sensu Khatri et al., 2010, 239–240―A. (A.) seriphidii, holotype, 241–245―A. (A.) acuteangulata, 246–247―A. (Oedicora) kerzhneri. 228, 230, 232, 234, 237, 239, 241–242, 246―penis, lateral view, 229, 231, 233, 235–236, 240, 243–245―male anal collar appendage, 238―end of pygofer lobe and male anal collar appendage, 247―end of pygofer lobe. 234–236―after Dubovsky (1967), 237–238―after Khatri et al. (2010)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4398510" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4398510/files/figure.png" pageId="23" pageNumber="273">Figs. 241–245</figureCitation>
