<bibRefCitation author="Logvinenko, V. N." box="[635,855,547,573]" pageId="23" pageNumber="273" pagination="19 - 27" refId="ref13586" refString="Logvinenko, V. N. (1984) New data on the fauna of Auchenorrhyncha (Homoptera) of Ukraine. In: Taxonomiya i zoogeografiya nasekomyh. Sbornik nauchnyh trudov. &quot; Naukova Dumka &quot;, Kiev, pp. 19 - 27. [in Russian]" type="book chapter" year="1984">Logvinenko (1984)</bibRefCitation>
