<bibRefCitation author="Mityaev, I. D." box="[868,1046,547,573]" pageId="23" pageNumber="273" refId="ref13797" refString="Mityaev, I. D. (1971) Cicadinea of Kazakhstan. Keys for identification of species. &quot; Nauka &quot; Publ., Alma-Ata, 211 pp. [in Russian]" type="book" year="1971">Mityaev (1971)</bibRefCitation>
